headline: ETFs Poised to Gain From Black Friday's $11.8B Online E-Commerce Sales
summary: SHOP and other e-commerce giants get a boost as Black Friday online spending hits a record $11.8B, lifting ETFs tied to digital retail demand.

headline: How is eBay’s Stock Performance Compared to Other Internet Stocks?
summary: eBay has significantly outpaced many of its industry peers over the past year, and analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook on the stock’s future performance.
